      *              * Per tutti i tipi documento: Fornitore           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-rg2-cod-con (1)      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc-rag (1)
                                          to   w-rg2-des-con (1)      .
       car-cat-rmc-cd1-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
