      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ref-iva-dar        to   w-rg2-cod-con (1)      .
           move      w-ref-iva-dar-des    to   w-rg2-des-con (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
