       car-cat-rmc-fd2-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se non esiste imposta deducibile                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-te2-tot-imp (1)    not  = zero          and
                     w-te2-tot-imp (1)    not  = w-te2-tot-ind (1)
                     go to car-cat-rmc-fd2-500.
       car-cat-rmc-fd2-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se bolla doganale                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
