                     go to car-cat-rmc-fd2-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di Dare/Avere                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "D"                  to   w-rg2-dar-ave (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento: Totale castelletto   *
      *                      *                    iva                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-te2-tot-doc (1)    to   w-rg2-imp-mov (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     car-cat-rmc-fd2-900.
       car-cat-rmc-fd2-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     car-cat-rmc-fd2-900.
       car-cat-rmc-fd2-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se esiste imposta deducibile                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se documento Italia                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test                                    *
