                     go to car-cat-rmc-fd2-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di Dare/Avere                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-tmf-tdo    =    03
                     move  "A"            to   w-rg2-dar-ave (1)
           else      move  "D"            to   w-rg2-dar-ave (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento: Totale imposta       *
      *                      *                    deducibile           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-te2-tot-ind (1)    from w-te2-tot-imp (1)
                                        giving w-rg2-imp-mov (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     car-cat-rmc-fd2-900.
       car-cat-rmc-fd2-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
